OL,3,CMatt Taylor returns to Exeter City as
OL,4,Cmanager until end of season
OL,6,FMatt Taylor has been confirmed as the
OL,7,Fnew manager of Exeter City, returning
OL,8,Fto the club he managed until four
OL,9,Fyears ago.
OL,11,FThe 44-year-old has been reappointed
OL,12,Fon an interim deal until the end of
OL,13,Fthe season. It comes after Gary
OL,14,FCaldwell left the club to join Wigan
OL,15,FAthletic in February.
OL,17,FTaylor will take over from Dan Green,
OL,18,Fwho took interim charge on 16 February.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
