OL,3,CMatt Taylor returns to Exeter City as
OL,4,Cmanager until end of season
OL,6,FThe former Grecians captain spent more
OL,7,Fthan four years in charge of Exeter
OL,8,Ffrom 2018, leading them out of League
OL,9,FTwo as runners-up in 2022 before
OL,10,Fjoining then Championship club
OL,11,FRotherham United later that year.
OL,13,FHe was sacked by the Millers after 13
OL,14,Fmonths before being hired by Bristol
OL,15,FRovers in December 2023.
OL,17,FThis is Taylor's first management job
OL,18,Fsince being sacked by Rovers in 2024.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
