OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1772572323
OL,3,CMatt Taylor returns to Exeter City as
OL,4,Cmanager until end of season
OL,6,F"I'm extremely pleased to return to
OL,7,FExeter City," Taylor said. "This Club
OL,8,Fand its supporters have always held a
OL,9,Fspecial place in my heart."
OL,11,FExeter City said the appointment has
OL,12,Fbeen made by the Club Board and in
OL,13,Fconsultation with the football
OL,14,Fmanagement team.
OL,16,F"We are delighted to welcome Matt back
OL,17,Fto the Club," Laurence Overend,
OL,18,Finterim club board chair, said.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
