OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,435,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1772572323
OL,3,CMatt Taylor returns to Exeter City as
OL,4,Cmanager until end of season
OL,6,F"He is someone who knows Exeter City
OL,7,Fexceptionally well and understands the
OL,8,FClub's culture, values and ambitions,
OL,9,Fas well as the realities of the league
OL,10,Fand our model."
OL,12,FMr Overend added: "Matt worked closely
OL,13,Fwith Dan and Kevin Nicholson during
OL,14,Fhis previous stint as manager, and it
OL,15,Fwas felt by the Club board that, as
OL,16,Fwell as bringing experience and
OL,17,Fexpertise, his appointment will
OL,18,Fminimise the amount of upheaval and
OL,19,Fchange for the squad, giving the
OL,20,Fplayers the confidence to finish the
OL,21,Fseason positively."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
