PN,43405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1772572323
OL,3,CMatt Taylor returns to Exeter City as
OL,4,Cmanager until end of season
OL,6,F"The Club and Trust boards would like
OL,7,Fto put on record their thanks to both
OL,8,FDan and Kevin for their continued
OL,9,Fcommitment and support to our Club."
OL,11,FTaylor joined Exeter City as a player
OL,12,Fin 2006 and made 160 appearances for
OL,13,Fthe Club between then and 2011.
OL,15,FHe will take the helm for tonight's
OL,16,Fmatch against Burton Albion and will
OL,17,Fbe assisted by Dan Green and Kevin
OL,18,FNicholson.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
