OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1772572323
OL,3,CMatt Taylor returns to Exeter City as
OL,4,Cmanager until end of season
OL,6,FTaylor added: "The (Exeter City)
OL,7,Fsupporters are like no other, and I'm
OL,8,Flooking forward to getting to know our
OL,9,Fplayers and staff and leading the team
OL,10,Fas we step out onto the pitch at St
OL,11,FJames Park tonight for the match
OL,12,Fagainst Burton Albion."
